  "description": {
    "zh": "又有些人报告说该地区又出现了邪教徒的活动。看起来他们中有些人又卷土重来了。这次我需要你从他们身上拿一些东西过来，无论他们带了什么，都有可能很有价值。拿到他们的装扮和那个奇怪的匕首，我不认为他们会免费送给你这些东西，所以你需要再次干掉他们……或者等别人为你干掉他们？拿到所有东西后你就可以回来了，再次祝你好运。",
    "en": "Some people reported cultist activities again in the area. Seems like some of them came back for more. Now the thing I need from you is some of their stuff, whatever they are carrying, it might be valuable. Obtain their attire and these weird daggers that they carry, I don't think they will give you their stuff for free tho so you need to kill them again... or wait till someone else does it for you. You can come back when you got all the stuff, good luck again."
  },
